  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TemplateContributor<AU>, Contexed, TableStructureContributer<AU>, HistoryFieldContributor, SummaryContributer<AU>, RemoteAuthListener<AU>

    public class ShibAttributeListener<AU extends AppUser>
extends AppUserComposite<AU,ShibAttributeListener>
implements RemoteAuthListener<AU>, SummaryContributer<AU>, TemplateContributor<AU>, HistoryFieldContributor
    Class to record request attributes (e.g. generated from shibboleth authentication) generated during external authentication.

    Config parameters:

    • tag.attributes - list of attribute names
    • tag.realm - authentication realms to listen to (comma seperated list)
    • attribute-name.label - alternative descriptive text for attr
